<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="freeze-on-large-search-traces">Freeze on Large Search Traces<a href="https://path-visualiser.github.io/blog/1.0.4#freeze-on-large-search-traces" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Freeze on Large Search Traces" title="Direct link to Freeze on Large Search Traces">​</a></h4>
<p>Posthoc may freeze when the search trace contains too many steps. This is due to the inefficient way the path is currently calculated.</p>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="cannot-choose-source-and-destination-nodes-for-queries-on-network-maps">Cannot Choose Source and Destination Nodes for Queries on Network Maps<a href="https://path-visualiser.github.io/blog/1.0.4#cannot-choose-source-and-destination-nodes-for-queries-on-network-maps" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Cannot Choose Source and Destination Nodes for Queries on Network Maps" title="Direct link to Cannot Choose Source and Destination Nodes for Queries on Network Maps">​</a></h4>
<p>Currently, queries on the network maps will force the source and destination nodes to be <code>0</code>.</p>]]></content>
